fields.title: Hello World
fields.content:
Welcome to CFE Django Blog


I wanted an easy way to launch a blog project from Django at anytime. That's what this is all about.

I'll continue to update the code on [github](https://github.com/codingforentrepreneurs/cfe-django-blog) to get it as production-ready as possible!



- Photo by: [Vladislav Klapin](https://unsplash.com/photos/PVr9Gsj93Pc?utm_source=unsplash&utm_medium=referral&utm_content=creditShareLink)
